==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scincoidian
<hw>Scin*coid"i*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Any one of numerous species of lizards of the family
<fam>Scincidae</fam> or tribe Scincoidea. The tongue is not extensile.
The body and tail are covered with overlapping scales, and the toes are
margined.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sciniph</ent>⟦br⟧
